        <label>Heavy Fire Support Mech Unit</label>
        <description>The heavy fire support Mech Unit serves primarily as an all-terrain platform for mounting heavy weaponry. According to reports, members of the MegaCorp Task Force experience an average 50% morale boost when advancing alongside one.</description>
